  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<p><u>General Support &amp; Housekeeping</u></p>\n<p>· Perform manual labour tasks within the company compound, including samples or marketing materials preparation, count and stock take samples and marketing materials, etc.</p>\n<p>· Ensure workplace cleanliness and safety</p>\n<p>· Assist and perform any other tasks as assigned by Production Supervisor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Communication and Teamwork skills</p>\n<p>· Preferably 1 – 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</p>\n<p>· Able to follow instructions &amp; work independently</p>\n<p>· Attention to details</p>\n<p>· Physically fit</p>\n<p>· Able to multi-task</p>\n<p>*driving license</p>\n<p>**5.5 days work week preferred</p>",
